com.google.gwt.uibinder.rebind
Class MortalLogger

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gwt.uibinder.rebind.MortalLogger

public class MortalLogger
extends java.lang.Object

Wraps a TreeLogger with handy String#format style methods and can be told to die. Perhaps we should instead add die(), warn(), etc. to Treelogger.
